msgstr "11800:[name]こずぴぃ[line]Kozupii! Is! Kozupii![%p]"

msgid "11900:[name]こずぴぃ[line]「それとこずぴぃは、“転校生”じゃなくて、折原梢、なのら」[%p]"
msgstr "11900:[name]こずぴぃ[line]Also, Kozupii's name isn't “transfer student,” it's Kozue Orihara, nora.[%p]"

msgid "12000:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "12000:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "12100:折原梢。そんな名前をだいぶ前に三住くんから聞いた覚えが、かすかにある。[%p]"
msgstr "12100:Kozue Orihara. I vaguely remembered hearing the name a long time ago from Misumi. Kozue...[%p]"

msgid "12200:梢。[linebreak]こずえ。[linebreak]こずぴぃ。[%p]"
msgstr "12200:Kozue... Kozupii.[%p]"

msgid "12300:まさか……。[%p]"
msgstr "12300:No way.[%p]"

msgid "12400:この声は、君が僕の頭の中に送り込んできているものっていうこと？[%p]"
msgstr "12400:So, you're sending this voice directly inside my head?[%p]"

msgid "12500:転校生はコクコクと一生懸命な様子でうなずく。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:She nodded again and again, as hard as she could.[%p]"

msgid "12600:[name]拓巳[line]「テ、テ、テレパシー……？」[%p]"
msgstr "12600:[name]拓巳[line]T-Telepathy?[%p]"

msgid "12700:[name]梢[line]「仕組みはよく分かんないのら」[%p]"
msgstr "12700:[name]梢[line]I don't know how it works, nora.[%p]"

msgid "12800:[name]梢[line]「でもできるのー」[%p]"
msgstr "12800:[name]梢[line]But I can do it![%p]"

msgid "12900:そんなバカな……。[%p]"
msgstr "12900:That's impossible.[%p]"

msgid "13000:声の正体は……彼女……だって言うの？[%p]"
msgstr "13000:So, this voice... was actually coming from the girl in front of me?[%p]"

msgid "13100:[name]梢[line]「西條くん、だーいじょうぶ？」[%p]"
msgstr "13100:[name]梢[line]Are you okay, Nishijo?[%p]"

msgid "13200:転校生はうつむいたまま、上目遣いで僕の顔を指差した。その指先が震えている。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:Her head was still slumped forward, but her eyes were turned up at me. She pointed a finger at my face. It was shaking.[%p]"

msgid "13300:[name]梢[line]「たらりーって、出てる」[%p]"
msgstr "13300:[name]梢[line]You're dripping.[%p]"

msgid "13400:自分の顔に触れてみた。[linebreak]鼻の下がぬるぬるする。鼻血が出ていた。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:I touched my face. The area under my nose was wet. My nose had been bleeding.[%p]"

msgid "13500:転校生がポケットティッシュを差し出してくる。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:She took out a pack of tissues from her pocket.[%p]"

msgid "13600:それを受け取って鼻血を拭きながらも、僕は薄気味悪さを覚えていた。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:I used it to wipe away the blood, feeling really creeped out.[%p]"

msgid "13700:転校生は――[%p]"
msgstr "13700:The transfer student—[%p]"

msgid "13800:[name]梢[line]「“こずぴぃ”だよ？」[%p]"
msgstr "13800:[name]梢[line]It's Kozupii, okay?[%p]"

msgid "13900:こ、こずぴぃは、口を動かしていない。喋ってない。[linebreak]それなのに、どうして僕には、彼女の声が聞こえるんだろう……。[%p]"
msgstr "13900:K-Kozupii's mouth wasn't moving. She wasn't speaking. So how could I hear her?[%p]"

msgid "14000:[name]梢[line]「心の声なのら」[%p]"
msgstr "14000:[name]梢[line]It's the voice of my heart, nora![%p]"

msgid "14100:そのウザい語尾はやめてくれ。三次元でやられると引く。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:Stop ending your sentences like that. It's weird when 3D girls do it.[%p]"

msgid "14200:[name]梢[line]「ふぇうっ、ご、ごめーん……」[%p]"
msgstr "14200:[name]梢[line]Waah... S-Sorry.[%p]"

msgid "14300:って、僕の心の声も聞こえるの！？[%p]"
msgstr "14300:Wait, you can hear my thoughts, too?[%p]"

msgid "14400:[name]梢[line]「聞こえるよ」[%p]"
msgstr "14400:[name]梢[line]I can![%p]"

msgid "14500:[name]拓巳[line]「ふ、普通に、話さないのは、な、なんで……？」[%p]"
msgstr "14500:[name]拓巳[line]W-Why don't you talk normally?[%p]"

msgid "14600:[name]梢[line]「…………っ」[%p]"
msgstr "14600:[name]梢[line]...[%p]"

msgid "14700:[name]梢[line]「恥ずかしいし……」[%p]"
msgstr "14700:[name]梢[line]I'm embarrassed.[%p]"

msgid "14800:そっか……。[linebreak]その気持ちはよく分かる。僕もそうだから。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:I see. I understood how that felt. I was the same way.[%p]"

msgid "14900:と、彼女は小動物っぽくキョロキョロとして、僕をチラリと見てからひとりで駅の方へ歩き出した。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:Her gaze suddenly darted back and forth like a little animal, before glancing at me and walking off toward the station on her own.[%p]"

msgid "15000:[name]梢[line]「ここー、離れた方がいいと思う」[%p]"
msgstr "15000:[name]梢[line]You should get away from here.[%p]"

msgid "15100:なんで？[linebreak]困惑しながらも僕は付いていく。[%p]"
msgstr "15100:Why? I followed, confused.[%p]"

msgid "15200:歩いていて気付いた。[%p]"
msgstr "15200:As I walked, I realized something.[%p]"

msgid "15300:脇腹に刺すような痛みがある。歩を進める度にズキズキとするから、僕はたまらず立ち止まった。[%p]"
msgstr "15300:There was a stabbing pain in my side. Each step I took ached so much that I had to stop.[%p]"

msgid "15400:脇腹をおさえ、息をつく。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:I held my side and took a moment to catch my breath.[%p]"

msgid "15500:人が多い。[linebreak]渋谷なんて大嫌いだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:There were so many people here. I hated Shibuya.[%p]"

msgid "15600:すれ違うすべての人に笑われている気がする。[linebreak]みんなに見られているような気がする。[%p]"
msgstr "15600:It felt like everybody I passed was laughing at me. It felt like everybody was looking at me.[%p]"

msgid "15700:みんなが僕の顔を知っているように思えてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "15700:It started to feel like everybody knew who I was.[%p]"

msgid "15800:――僕を、見るな。[linebreak]――僕を、笑うな。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:—Don't look at me. —Don't laugh at me.[%p]"

msgid "15900:どこか、人のいないところで休みたい……。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:I need to rest somewhere without a lot of people around.[%p]"

msgid "16000:[name]梢[line]「ほいじゃあ、いーいところがあるのら！」[%p]"
msgstr "16000:[name]梢[line]I know just the place, nora![%p]"

msgid "16100:[name]梢[line]「ごあんなーい、します♪」[%p]"
msgstr "16100:[name]梢[line]Let me show you! ♪[%p]"

msgid "16200:こずぴぃは、学校で何度か顔を合わせていたときとは、明らかにテンションが違った。[%p]"
msgstr "16200:I'd only met Kozupii a few times at school, but now she was like a completely different person.[%p]"

msgid "16300:それにリアルでは無口なのに、心の声は、こんなにも、その……[%p]"
msgstr "16300:And even though in the real world she was completely silent, in her mind she was...[%p]"

msgid "16400:[name]梢[line]「あっ、今、うるさーい女って考えたー！\u3000うぷー！」[%p]"
msgstr "16400:[name]梢[line]You just thought I was annoying, didn't you! Uboooh![%p]"

msgid "16500:……心の声で話ができるっていうのは、便利だけど、鬱陶しい。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:It was convenient to be able to talk to somebody mentally, but it was also obnoxious.[%p]"

msgid "16600:っていうか、僕もあっさり受け入れちゃってるけど、これっていったいどういう仕組みなんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "16600:And wait a second, how did this even work?[%p]"

msgid "16700:まさか本物の超能力……？[%p]"
msgstr "16700:Was it a real psychic power?[%p]"

msgid "16800:[name]梢[line]「やっぱり、こずぴぃのこと、気味悪い……よね」[%p]"
msgstr "16800:[name]梢[line]You think Kozupii's creepy... don't you?[%p]"

msgid "16900:[name]梢[line]「こんなの、普通じゃないし……」[%p]"
msgstr "16900:[name]梢[line]I know this isn't normal...[%p]"

msgid "17000:……普通じゃないのは、別に気にしてないよ。[linebreak]他にも変人と遭遇する機会が最近増えたし。[%p]"
msgstr "17000:The fact that it's not normal doesn't really bother me. I've met a lot of weird people lately.[%p]"

msgid "17100:それにこずぴぃは、口調はちょっと変だけど、怖いわけでも、デンパなわけでもないから、まだマシだよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:And you might talk funny, but you're not scary or crazy. So, you're a lot better than some of them.[%p]"

msgid "17200:[name]梢[line]「そう言ってもらえると、うるうるーってなっちゃうのら……」[%p]"
msgstr "17200:[name]梢[line]Saying that makes my eyes tear up, nora...[%p]"

msgid "17300:歩きながらこずぴぃはいきなり泣き出す。[linebreak]驚いて、僕は慌ててポケットティッシュを返した。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:Kozupii suddenly started to cry as she walked. Surprised, I handed back the tissues.[%p]"

msgid "17400:[name]梢[line]「…………っ」[%p]"
msgstr "17400:[name]梢[line]...[%p]"

msgid "17500:彼女はペコペコと必要以上に頭を下げてそれを受け取り、目元の涙を拭った。[%p]"
msgstr "17500:She wiped her eyes with one of them, giving me a bow that was deeper than it needed to be.[%p]"

msgid "17600:……さっきの続きだけど。[%p]"
msgstr "17600:So, anyway...[%p]"

msgid "17700:考えてることを全部読まれちゃうのは、気味が悪いし、居心地も悪い。[linebreak]それが、率直な感想。[%p]"
msgstr "17700:Having you read all my thoughts is creepy, and uncomfortable, too. That's my honest opinion.[%p]"

msgid "17800:[name]梢[line]「そーだよね……」[%p]"
msgstr "17800:[name]梢[line]Yeah, yeah...[%p]"

msgid "17900:[name]梢[line]「ごめんなしゃい……」[%p]"
msgstr "17900:[name]梢[line]I'm sowwy.[%p]"

msgid "18000:[name]梢[line]「でーもでーも、聞きたくなくても聞こえちゃうの……うにゅ〜」[%p]"
msgstr "18000:[name]梢[line]But! But! I hear people's thoughts even when I don't want to. Unyuh...[%p]"

msgid "18100:そう、なの……？[%p]"
msgstr "18100:Is that... true?[%p]"

msgid "18200:[name]梢[line]「そなの」[%p]"
msgstr "18200:[name]梢[line]It's true.[%p]"

msgid "18300:まあ、なんにせよ君も僕みたいなキモオタに[linebreak]そんなこと言われたくないよね……。[%p]"
msgstr "18300:Well, I'm sure you don't want to hear that from a creepy otaku... like me, of course.[%p]"

msgid "18400:こんなキモい男には、やっぱり価値なんてない……。[%p]"
msgstr "18400:I'm a creepy loser. And totally worthless.[%p]"

msgid "18500:[name]梢[line]「そーんなことない！」[%p]"
msgstr "18500:[name]梢[line]That's not true![%p]"

msgid "18600:鬱モードに戻りかけたところで、こずぴぃが心の声で強く叫んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "18600:Just as I was starting to go back into depression mode, I heard Kozupii shout in my mind.[%p]"

msgid "18700:[name]梢[line]「ダーメだよ、そんなこと、言っちゃ」[%p]"
msgstr "18700:[name]梢[line]Don't say that stuff![%p]"

msgid "18800:[name]梢[line]「そんな、悲しいこと……」[%p]"
msgstr "18800:[name]梢[line]It's so... sad.[%p]"

msgid "18900:[name]梢[line]「……っ、……」[%p]"
msgstr "18900:[name]梢[line]…[%p]"

msgid "19000:またはらはらと泣き始める。[%p]"
msgstr "19000:She started crying again.[%p]"

msgid "19100:なんで泣くの？[linebreak]僕に同情してるの？[%p]"
msgstr "19100:Why are you crying? Are you pitying me?[%p]"

msgid "19200:だとしたらそんなの必要ないよ。[%p]"
msgstr "19200:If so, then you don't need to do that.[%p]"

msgid "19300:なにしろ僕は、妄想で脳内人格を作り出して、それが実在してる人物だって勘違いしちゃうぐらいなんだ。例えば梨深とか……。[%p]"
msgstr "19300:I'm such a weirdo, I make up girls in my head and pretend they're real. Like Rimi...[%p]"

msgid "19400:[name]梢[line]「それって、咲畑しゃん……じゃなかった、咲畑さんのこーと？」[%p]"
msgstr "19400:[name]梢[line]You mean… Sakihata?[%p]"

msgid "19500:知ってるの！？[%p]"
msgstr "19500:You know her?[%p]"

msgid "19600:[name]梢[line]「だって、クラスメイトだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "19600:[name]梢[line]She's in our class![%p]"

msgid "19700:[name]梢[line]「西條くんのー、カノジョしゃんなのら」[%p]"
msgstr "19700:[name]梢[line]She's your girlfriend, nora![%p]"

msgid "19800:ち、違うよ……！[%p]"
msgstr "19800:N-No she's not.[%p]"

msgid "19900:[name]梢[line]「違うのー？\u3000てっきりてっきり、そうだとばーぁっかり思ってた」[%p]"
msgstr "19900:[name]梢[line]She's not? I was soooo sure she was.[%p]"

msgid "20000:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "20000:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "20100:こずぴぃが、梨深のことを知っている。[linebreak]それが意味するのは――[%p]"
msgstr "20100:Kozupii knew Rimi. That could only mean one thing.[%p]"

msgid "20200:梨深は、実在してるっていうこと。[%p]"
msgstr "20200:Rimi was real.[%p]"

msgid "20300:僕の妄想じゃない。[linebreak]僕の脳内キャラじゃない。[linebreak]梨深は、ちゃんと、いるんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "20300:She wasn't a delusion. She wasn't somebody I'd invented in my head. She was a real person.[%p]"

msgid "20400:[name]拓巳[line]「そう、か……」[%p]"
msgstr "20400:[name]拓巳[line]Oh...[%p]"

msgid "20500:よかった……。[%p]"
msgstr "20500:Whew.[%p]"

msgid "20600:でも、だとしたらどうして、一度も連絡をくれないんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "20600:But then why wouldn't she make any effort to contact me?[%p]"

msgid "20700:やっぱり、あのＯ－ＦＲＯＮＴの一件で、梨深にも愛想を尽かされちゃったのかな。[%p]"
msgstr "20700:Maybe she'd given up on me after what happened at O-FRONT.[%p]"

msgid "20800:[name]梢[line]「咲畑しゃん、地震があったあの日、青い顔をして早退していっちゃったのら」[%p]"
msgstr "20800:[name]梢[line]Sakihata got really worried about something the day of the earthquake and left school early.[%p]"

msgid "20900:[name]梢[line]「それ以来、学校来てなーいよ？」[%p]"
msgstr "20900:[name]梢[line]She hasn't been back to school since then.[%p]"

msgid "21000:[name]梢[line]「もしかして、家族になにか悲しーいことがあった……かも〜」[%p]"
msgstr "21000:[name]梢[line]Maybe something sad happened to her family…[%p]"

msgid "21100:そう……なんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "21100:Oh...[%p]"

msgid "21200:救われた気分になった。僕は梨深に見捨てられたわけじゃないって分かったら、本気で涙が出そうになった。[%p]"
msgstr "21200:I felt so much better. Knowing that Rimi hadn't given up on me after all made me feel like I was really going to cry.[%p]"

msgid "21300:そういうことなら、また、学校に行く理由ができた。梨深にもう一度会いたい。それまでは、頑張って、学校に行こう――[%p]"
msgstr "21300:I had a reason to go to school again. I wanted to see Rimi. Until she came back, I would keep forcing myself to go to school every day.[%p]"

msgid "21400:[name]梢[line]「気をつけーてね」[%p]"
msgstr "21400:[name]梢[line]Be careful, okay?[%p]"

msgid "21500:え……？[%p]"
msgstr "21500:Huh?[%p]"

msgid "21600:[name]梢[line]「西條くんがー、咲畑しゃんと付き合ってるって思ってたから、言わなかったけどけどけどー」[%p]"
msgstr "21600:[name]梢[line]I didn't say anything because I thought she was your girlfriend, but… but… but…[%p]"

msgid "21700:[name]梢[line]「咲畑しゃんには、気をつけて」[%p]"
msgstr "21700:[name]梢[line]You should be careful around Sakihata.[%p]"

msgid "21800:どういう、意味……？[%p]"
msgstr "21800:What does that mean?[%p]"

msgid "21900:[name]梢[line]「咲畑しゃんは、よく分かんないのら……」[%p]"
msgstr "21900:[name]梢[line]I don't really understand her, nora.[%p]"

msgid "22000:だから、どういう意味だよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "22000:What does that mean, though?[%p]"

msgid "22100:よく分からない、って――[%p]"
msgstr "22100:You don't understand her?[%p]"

msgid "22200:あの『張り付け』のこと？[%p]"
msgstr "22200:You mean the Crucified murder?[%p]"

msgid "22300:それとも、彼女と１年生の頃からクラスメートだったっていう事実が僕の記憶から欠落してること？[%p]"
msgstr "22300:Or are you talking about how all my memories of her being my classmate since our first year were missing?[%p]"

msgid "22400:確かに梨深には、いまだに謎の部分がある。[%p]"
msgstr "22400:She was still mysterious in a lot of ways, sure.[%p]"

msgid "22500:でも彼女は、僕を何度も助けてくれた。[linebreak]怯えてた僕に“一緒にいてあげる”って言ってくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "22500:But she'd been there for me so many times. When I was scared, she offered to be by my side.[%p]"

msgid "22600:彼女は僕の敵じゃない……！[%p]"
msgstr "22600:She wasn't my enemy![%p]"

msgid "22700:[name]梢[line]「ひゃう〜〜」[%p]"
msgstr "22700:[name]梢[line]Hyauuh![%p]"

msgid "22800:なぜかこずぴぃは目を回していた。[%p]"
msgstr "22800:For some reason, Kozupii looked dizzy.[%p]"

msgid "22900:[name]梢[line]「そんなに一度にいっぱぁい考えらーれると……」[%p]"
msgstr "22900:[name]梢[line]If you think all those thoughts at once...[%p]"

msgid "23000:[name]梢[line]「こずぴぃ、ついていけにゃい〜」[%p]"
msgstr "23000:[name]梢[line]Kozupii can't keep up.[%p]"

msgid "23100:ご、ごめん……。[%p]"
msgstr "23100:S-Sorry...[%p]"

msgid "23200:なんだか不思議だ。[%p]"
msgstr "23200:It was kind of strange.[%p]"

msgid "23300:僕はいつも、誰かと会話するときは考えていることの２割も言えないで終わっちゃうことがほとんどだったけど、心の会話じゃむしろ“喋りすぎ”ならぬ“考えすぎ”っていうことになっちゃうのかも。[%p]"
msgstr "23300:When I was talking to people, I always had trouble getting out even a fifth of what I was trying to say. But talking like this might mean I'd have to work on not thinking too much.[%p]"

msgid "23400:こずぴぃにしてもそうだ。[%p]"
msgstr "23400:It was probably the same for Kozupii.[%p]"

msgid "23500:まさかこんなに――脳内で――喋る子だとは思わなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "23500:I didn't think she'd talk so much in her mind.[%p]"

msgid "23600:[name]梢[line]「喋ってる、っていう感覚は薄ーいよ？」[%p]"
msgstr "23600:[name]梢[line]It doesn't really feel like I'm talking, though?[%p]"

msgid "23700:[name]梢[line]「考えてるだけ。それが流れ込むだけ。[linebreak]相手にはビビーッて。相手からはドバーッて」[%p]"
msgstr "23700:[name]梢[line]It's just thinking. And listening. I go beep-beep! And they go boop-boop.[%p]"

msgid "23800:[name]梢[line]「慣れてないと、自分の思考と相手の思考がごちゃごちゃーってなって、うにゃあ？\u3000ってなるの」[%p]"
msgstr "23800:[name]梢[line]If you're not used to it, your thoughts and their thoughts get mixed up, and then you go unyah![%p]"

msgid "23900:に、日本語でおｋ……。[%p]"
msgstr "23900:Plz 2 spk Japanese kthx.[%p]"

msgid "24000:ニュアンスとしてはなんとなく理解できるけど。[%p]"
msgstr "24000:I mean, I kind of get the nuance, but...[%p]"

msgid "24100:会話の機微みたいなものがない、っていうことかな。[%p]"
msgstr "24100:I guess she meant that there are none of the more subtle points of conversation.[%p]"

msgid "24200:相手の顔色を窺って、言いたいことが言えなくなっちゃう、なんてこともない。[%p]"
msgstr "24200:And you never have to worry about being too scared about what the other person would think, and not being able to say what you wanted to say.[%p]"

msgid "24300:考えてることが駄々漏れなら、“空気を読む”ことさえできなくなるよね。[%p]"
msgstr "24300:You couldn't try to “read the room” if every single thought you had was being shared.[%p]"

msgid "24400:一方通行じゃないけど、双方向でもなくて、てんでバラバラに飛び交っている矢印を選んで他は聞かないようにしなきゃいけない、みたいなことなのかも。[%p]"
msgstr "24400:It wasn't one-way communication, but maybe it wasn't two-way communication, either. Maybe it was like trying to focus on one out of a million things at once, and ignoring the rest.[%p]"

msgid "24500:[name]梢[line]「だからだーから、気楽だし、距離感も近いけど――」[%p]"
msgstr "24500:[name]梢[line]And so, and so... it's easy, and you feel really close to people! But…[%p]"

msgid "24600:[name]梢[line]「傷つくことも、簡単なの」[%p]"
msgstr "24600:[name]梢[line]It's easy to get hurt.[%p]"

msgid "24700:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "24700:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "24800:一瞬、こずぴぃは表情を曇らせた。[linebreak]でもすぐに、泣き笑いのような表情を浮かべる。[%p]"
msgstr "24800:She frowned for a moment. But then an expression appeared on her face that was halfway between a smile and a sob.[%p]"

msgid "24900:[name]梢[line]「えへ。西條くんは初めてなのにすーんごく上手だよー」[%p]"
msgstr "24900:[name]梢[line]Ehehe! It's your first time, Nishijo, but you're really good at this![%p]"

msgid "25000:[name]梢[line]「こずぴぃとビビビが合うの」[%p]"
msgstr "25000:[name]梢[line]Kozupii and you have the same beep-beep-beep![%p]"

msgid "25100:ビビビが、ね……。[linebreak]波長が合う、って言いたいのかな？[%p]"
msgstr "25100:Beep-beep-beep, huh? Maybe she was saying we were on the same wavelength?[%p]"

msgid "25200:[name]梢[line]「そーう。はちょーはちょー」[%p]"
msgstr "25200:[name]梢[line]Yup! Wavelength! That's right![%p]"

msgid "25300:まあ、星来たん相手にいつも似たようなことやってるからじゃないかな……。[%p]"
msgstr "25300:Well, I was always having similar conversations in my head with Seira-tan. Maybe that was why.[%p]"

msgid "25400:[name]梢[line]「あ、でもでもー、あのときの西條くんは怖かったの。うぴぃ」[%p]"
msgstr "25400:[name]梢[line]Oh, but! But! You were really scary then, Nishijo. Upiiih.[%p]"

msgid "25500:あのとき……？[%p]"
msgstr "25500:Then?[%p]"

msgid "25600:[name]梢[line]「今日の朝、教室で」[%p]"
msgstr "25600:[name]梢[line]This morning. In the classroom.[%p]"

msgid "25700:げ、そ、そう言えば……[linebreak]僕ってばむちゃくちゃやばい妄想をしてたような。[%p]"
msgstr "25700:Crap. C-Come to think of it... I'd had some really weird, nasty delusions.[%p]"

msgid "25800:[name]梢[line]「だから、ふひゃーって思って、つい声をかけちゃったのら……」[%p]"
msgstr "25800:[name]梢[line]So, I went “Fyaaah!” and actually decided to talk to you, nora.[%p]"

msgid "25900:[name]梢[line]「ほんとーは、なるべくこの力を他の人に知られないようにしーようって、決めてたのに」[%p]"
msgstr "25900:[name]梢[line]Usually, I try to make sure that nobody finds out about my power.[%p]"

msgid "26000:いや、あのときは、自暴自棄になってたっていうか……えと、えと……まぁ……あくまで妄想というか……はは……[%p]"
msgstr "26000:No, um... I was kind of in a bad place then... and well... it was just a delusion. Haha...[%p]"

msgid "26100:軽蔑するよね、普通。[linebreak]はあ……。[%p]"
msgstr "26100:Yeah... Most people would find that disgusting. Sigh...[%p]"

msgid "26200:[name]梢[line]「きっと、それをほんっとーにやってたら、こずぴぃは西條くんを――」[%p]"
msgstr "26200:[name]梢[line]If you'd actually done any of that stuff, Kozupii would've…[%p]"

msgid "26300:[name]梢[line]「殺してたよ♪」[%p]"
msgstr "26300:[name]梢[line]killed you! ♪[%p]"

msgid "26400:……え？[%p]"
msgstr "26400:...Huh?[%p]"

msgid "26500:あまりにも無邪気に、そんな物騒なことを言うから。[linebreak]そのギャップに、僕は、ゾクリとした。[%p]"
msgstr "26500:The gap between her tone and her words made me shiver.[%p]"

msgid "26600:僕らは無言のまま――でも心での交信は続けながら――センター街を抜けて井の頭通りに出た。[%p]"
msgstr "26600:We walked through Center Street silently, talking to each other in our minds, and headed out to Inokashira Street.[%p]"

msgid "26700:僕らって、傍目から見ると、無言のまま互いの顔も見ずに歩いている、初々しいカップルに見えるのかな。[%p]"
msgstr "26700:If you didn't know the truth, you might think from the way that we were walking along silently, without really looking at each other, that we were were a couple that had just started dating.[%p]"

msgid "26800:[name]梢[line]「っ！」[%p]"
msgstr "26800:[name]梢[line]...![%p]"

msgid "26900:隣でこずぴぃが盛大に息を呑む。[linebreak]そして目を丸くして、僕の顔を見上げてきた。[%p]"
msgstr "26900:Kozupii let out a gasp next to me. Her eyes went wide as she looked up at me.[%p]"

msgid "27000:[name]梢[line]「カ、カップル……」[%p]"
msgstr "27000:[name]梢[line]A-A couple...![%p]"

msgid "27100:ち、違う！\u3000あくまで例えだよ、た・と・え！[%p]"
msgstr "27100:N-No! It was just a hypothetical![%p]"

msgid "27200:[name]梢[line]「またふひゃーってさせられたのらー」[%p]"
msgstr "27200:[name]梢[line]You made me go “Fyaaah!” again, nora![%p]"

msgid "27300:[name]梢[line]「西條くんにラブラブラーブ告白されたかと……」[%p]"
msgstr "27300:[name]梢[line]I thought you were telling me you were in love with me![%p]"

msgid "27400:ご、ごめん……。[%p]"
msgstr "27400:S-Sorry...[%p]"

msgid "27500:やっぱり全部筒抜けだとやりにくい……。[linebreak]こずぴぃと話してるときは、余計な妄想はできるだけしない方が身のためかも。[%p]"
msgstr "27500:It's hard when somebody can hear your every thought. It was probably best to keep my delusions to a minimum when talking to Kozupii.[%p]"

msgid "27600:[name]梢[line]「あのーあのー、聞きたいな」[%p]"
msgstr "27600:[name]梢[line]Um, um... I want to ask![%p]"

msgid "27700:[name]梢[line]「先週の、西條くんがテレビに出てたときのこと」[%p]"
msgstr "27700:[name]梢[line]About when you were on TV last week.[%p]"

msgid "27800:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "27800:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "27900:……どうせ、言ったって信じてくれないよ。[%p]"
msgstr "27900:You wouldn't believe me if I told you.[%p]"

msgid "28000:[name]梢[line]「それ決めつけー。うぷー」[%p]"
msgstr "28000:[name]梢[line]You don't know that! Uboooh![%p]"

msgid "28100:[name]梢[line]「こずぴぃは、あのとき下にいたんだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "28100:[name]梢[line]Kozupii was down there below you that night.[%p]"

msgid "28200:下……？[%p]"
msgstr "28200:Below?[%p]"

msgid "28300:[name]梢[line]「スクランブル交差点。ハチ公口の改札前。ちょうど、通りかかって」[%p]"
msgstr "28300:[name]梢[line]In Scramble Crossing. In front of the turnstiles at the Hachiko exit. I was passing through right when it happened.[%p]"

msgid "28400:[name]梢[line]「あのとき、ずっと声、聞こえーてたよ」[%p]"
msgstr "28400:[name]梢[line]I could hear a voice the whole time.[%p]"

msgid "28500:[name]梢[line]「西條くんの、声」[%p]"
msgstr "28500:[name]梢[line]It was your voice.[%p]"

msgid "28600:[name]梢[line]「七海しゃんを助けたい、助けなきゃ、って」[%p]"
msgstr "28600:[name]梢[line]It said, “I want to save Nanami. I have to save her!”[%p]"

msgid "28700:[name]梢[line]「聞こえたよ」[%p]"
msgstr "28700:[name]梢[line]I heard it.[%p]"

msgid "28800:僕の心の声は、そんな遠くまで届いたの？[linebreak]Ｏ－ＦＲＯＮＴの屋上から駅の改札まで、意外と距離あるけど。[%p]"
msgstr "28800:My thoughts carried that far? There was a pretty big distance between the roof of O-FRONT and the turnstiles at the station.[%p]"

msgid "28900:[name]梢[line]「それだけ、あのときの西條くんの想いは、強かったーのら」[%p]"
msgstr "28900:[name]梢[line]Your feelings were just that strong![%p]"

msgid "29000:じゃあ、こずぴぃは分かってくれるんだね。[%p]"
msgstr "29000:So, you would know, then.[%p]"

msgid "29100:僕が、超能力のパフォーマンスをやるつもりであんな騒動を起こしたわけじゃないって。[%p]"
msgstr "29100:You'd know I wasn't up there pretending to be a psychic for attention.[%p]"

msgid "29200:[name]梢[line]「うん。だからだーから、価値はなくなくないよ。"
msgstr "29200:[name]梢[line]Yeah. So, so, you're not not not worthless!"

msgid "29300:う？\u3000なくなく？」[%p]"
msgstr "29300: Huh? Not not not?[%p]"

msgid "29400:[name]梢[line]「うん。だからだーから、価値はなくなくないよ。う？\u3000なくなく？」"
msgstr "29400:[name]梢[line]Yeah. So, so, you don't not have value! Huh? “Don't not?”"

msgid "29500:でも……結局、ダメだったんだ。[linebreak]僕は七海を……妹を助けるよりも、自分の命を優先した。[linebreak]ギリギリになって、逃げた……。[%p]"
msgstr "29500:But... in the end, I failed. I chose to save my own life instead of saving hers. I ran away at the last minute.[%p]"

msgid "29600:こずぴぃは、Ｒｏｆｔの前で立ち止まった。[linebreak]その入り口を指差しながら、僕を見る。[%p]"
msgstr "29600:Kozupii stopped right in front of the Roft building. She pointed at the entrance as she looked at me.[%p]"

msgid "29700:どうやら“案内する”って言ってたのは、この中らしい。[%p]"
msgstr "29700:This was, evidently, the place she'd wanted to take me.[%p]"

msgid "29800:Ｒｏｆｔの中に休む場所なんてあるとは思えない。[%p]"
msgstr "29800:Roft was a store that sold cosmetics, kitchenware, and little knick-knacks. I couldn't imagine there being any place to rest there.[%p]"

msgid "29900:それに狭い密閉空間に、客がいっぱいだ。[%p]"
msgstr "29900:It was a cramped space that was filled with people.[%p]"

msgid "30000:……無意識のうちに足が震えていた。[linebreak]あの夜のスクランブル交差点で聞いた歓声や怒声が、頭の中に響いてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "30000:My legs were shaking. The cheers and angry yells I'd heard that night in Scramble Crossing started to echo in my head.[%p]"

msgid "30100:人が多い場所には行きたくない……。[linebreak]Ｒｏｆｔの中に入ったら、逃げ場がなくなる……。[%p]"
msgstr "30100:I didn't want to go anywhere with so many people around. If I went inside the Roft, there'd be nowhere to run.[%p]"

msgid "30200:[name]梢[line]「だーいじょうぶだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "30200:[name]梢[line]It'll be okay![%p]"

msgid "30300:彼女は僕が怯えているにもかかわらず、それを無視してどんどん先に歩いていく。[%p]"
msgstr "30300:She ignored my fear and headed inside.[%p]"

msgid "30400:僕はできるだけ周囲を見ないようにしながら、足早についていくしかなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "30400:I had no choice but to quickly follow, trying my best not to look at the people around me.[%p]"

msgid "30500:上りエスカレーターに乗ると、こずぴぃは後ろに立つ僕に振り返った。小柄な彼女は一段上にいて、それでちょうど背の高さが同じぐらいになった。[%p]"
msgstr "30500:When we got on the up escalator, Kozupii turned around to look at me. She was a step above me, but she was so tiny we were at about the same height.[%p]"

msgid "30600:[name]梢[line]「七海しゃんは助かったんだよね？\u3000だーったら、西條くんが頑張ったおかげだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "30600:[name]梢[line]Nanami's safe though, right? If she is, it's because of you.[%p]"

msgid "30700:僕の力で助かったわけじゃない。[linebreak]僕はなにもしてないのと同じだよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "30700:I hadn't been the one to save her. I hadn't really done anything.[%p]"

msgid "30800:[name]梢[line]「屋上から、手を伸ーばしてたよね？」[%p]"
msgstr "30800:[name]梢[line]You were reaching out off the roof, weren't you?[%p]"

msgid "30900:[name]梢[line]「なにを、しようとしたの？」[%p]"
msgstr "30900:[name]梢[line]What were you trying to do?[%p]"

msgid "31000:[name]梢[line]「びょーんって、飛ぼうとしたのかな？」[%p]"
msgstr "31000:[name]梢[line]Were you trying to hop off and fly?[%p]"

msgid "31100:……違うよ。[linebreak]剣を、手に入れようとしてた。[%p]"
msgstr "31100:No. I was trying to get a sword.[%p]"

msgid "31200:それは妄想の剣で、あの屋上から見た景色の中に溶け込んでて。[%p]"
msgstr "31200:It's made out of delusions, and I could kind of see it from up there on the roof.[%p]"

msgid "31300:[name]梢[line]「ディソード？」[%p]"
msgstr "31300:[name]梢[line]A Di-Sword?[%p]"

msgid "31400:うん。そう。[linebreak]手を伸ばせばつかめるって言われたけど、できなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "31400:Yeah. That's right. They said if I stretched out my hand, I could grab it. But it didn't work.[%p]"

msgid "31500:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "31500:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "31600:[name]拓巳[line]「な、なんで……っ！？」[%p]"
msgstr "31600:[name]拓巳[line]H-How?[%p]"

msgid "31700:思わず叫んでしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "31700:I suddenly shouted aloud.[%p]"

msgid "31800:すれ違う下りエスカレーターに乗っていたカップルに、冷たい目を向けられて、慌てて自分の口を手で押さえる。[%p]"
msgstr "31800:A couple on the down escalator opposite us glared at me, and I quickly put my hand over my mouth.[%p]"

msgid "31900:……こずぴぃ、なんでディソードのこと、知ってるの？[%p]"
msgstr "31900:Kozupii, how do you know about the Di-Swords?[%p]"

msgid "32000:[name]梢[line]「こずぴぃも持ってーるもん」[%p]"
msgstr "32000:[name]梢[line]Kozupii has one, too![%p]"

msgid "32100:[name]拓巳[line]「へ……？」[%p]"
msgstr "32100:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "32200:５階でエスカレーターを降りると、こずぴぃは何気なく右手を頭上に掲げた。[%p]"
msgstr "32200:We got off the escalator at the fifth floor, and Kozupii casually raised her right hand above her head.[%p]"

msgid "32300:その仕草はまるで、太陽のまぶしさに対して手でひさしを作っているかのようで。[%p]"
msgstr "32300:It was just like she was trying to block out the brightness of the sun.[%p]"

msgid "32400:その手に沿うように、いきなり空中に光が出現する。[%p]"
msgstr "32400:Suddenly, a light appeared in midair next to her hand.[%p]"

msgid "32500:いや、それは光というより、線。[%p]"
msgstr "32500:No, it wasn't a light. It was a line.[%p]"

msgid "32600:例えるなら、ワイヤーフレームに似ていた。[%p]"
msgstr "32600:You could say it looked like a wireframe.[%p]"

msgid "32700:いくつもの光線がなにもなかったはずの空間に交錯し、やがて形作ったのは、スノーボードのような形状。[%p]"
msgstr "32700:Rays of light overlapped in what had only a moment ago been empty space, forming something that looked like a snowboard.[%p]"

msgid "32800:そこへ、青い光――ワイヤーフレームの光線よりも輝きが激しい――が幾筋か走り。[%p]"
msgstr "32800:Then, rays of blue light, brighter than the rays of the wireframe, streamed out of it.[%p]"

msgid "32900:こずぴぃが、開いていた手を握りしめた。[%p]"
msgstr "32900:Kozupii closed her opened hand.[%p]"

msgid "33000:直後、ワイヤーフレームだったものが、[%p]"
msgstr "33000:What had been a wireframe,[%p]"

msgid "33100:テクスチャを貼ったかのように、[%p]"
msgstr "33100:instead became a heavy, cold slab of metal,[%p]"

msgid "33200:重厚さと冷たさを感じさせる金属の板へと姿を変えていた。[%p]"
msgstr "33200:like someone had pasted textures on it.[%p]"

msgid "33300:[name]拓巳[line]「ディ……ソード……！」[%p]"
msgstr "33300:[name]拓巳[line]A Di-Sword...[%p]"

msgid "33400:セナやあやせが持っていたものと、形状はあまりにもかけ離れているけど。[linebreak]それでも、身に纏う空気は同じだった。[%p]"
msgstr "33400:It looked completely different than the ones Ayase and Sena had. But it had the same kind of intensity about it.[%p]"

msgid "33500:板、というにはあまりに禍々しく。[%p]"
msgstr "33500:It was far too malevolent to be a simple board.[%p]"

msgid "33600:剣、というにはあまりにも飾り気がなく。[%p]"
msgstr "33600:And far too unadorned to be a sword.[%p]"

msgid "33700:無垢なる獰猛さと。[linebreak]破滅的な凛々しさとを持ち合わせているそれを。[%p]"
msgstr "33700:It combined an innocent ferocity... with a destructive beauty.[%p]"

msgid "33800:彼女は、軽々と掲げ持っている。[%p]"
msgstr "33800:And she held it above her like it weighed nothing at all.[%p]"

